            A glimpse into the YURA archive — watches, eyewear, and durags handpicked for
            the vault.
          </p>
        </div>
      </header>

      {error ? (
        <p className="products-error" role="status">
          {error}
        </p>
      ) : data.length === 0 ? (
        <p className="products-empty" role="status">
          No products are available yet. Secure entries will appear here once your vault
